## 4. Post-migration layout (target)

```
zedos.app/                                       (workspace root)
├── apps/
│   └── web/                                     (the Next.js app — moved from zedos/nextjs_space/)
│       ├── app/                                 (App Router — routes + pages)
│       ├── lib/composition.ts                   (per-app composition root)
│       ├── e2e/                                 (Playwright — Phase 4)
│       └── package.json
├── packages/
│   ├── tsconfig/                                (base.json, nextjs.json, node.json, test.json)
│   ├── eslint-config/                           (base.cjs, next.cjs, react.cjs, boundaries.cjs)
│   ├── vitestconfig/                            (shared Vitest preset)
│   ├── domain/                                  (entities, ports, domain services)
│   ├── application/                             (use cases)
│   ├── contracts/                               (zod schemas — single source of truth)
│   ├── persistence/                             (Drizzle adapters — replaces Prisma adapters per Phase 3)
│   ├── shared/                                  (Result, errors, logger — neverthrow-backed)
│   ├── ui/                                      (shadcn-ish design system + Storybook)
│   ├── auth/                                    (better-auth options, type augmentation, adapters)
│   ├── sdk-stripe/                              (vendor wrapper — Result<T> + zod-validated responses)
│   ├── sdk-ai/                                  (vendor wrapper — provider-abstracted)
│   ├── database/                                (drizzle schema + migrations — replaces zedos/nextjs_space/prisma/)
│   └── result/                                  (neverthrow re-export + helpers, if not folded into shared/)
├── services/                                    (only if/when async runtime units are justified — out of v0)
├── prisma/                                      (transitional — exists only during Phase 1–2 if Drizzle migration is staged)
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml
├── turbo.jsonc
├── .changeset/
└── syncpack.config.js
```

### Stack decisions locked for the post-migration target

| Concern | Choice | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| Package manager | pnpm | `71-monorepo-context.mdc` (this rule) |
| Task runner | Turborepo | `71-monorepo-context.mdc` |
| ORM | Drizzle (replacing Prisma) | `75-drizzle.mdc` |
| Auth | better-auth | `76-better-auth.mdc` |
| Framework | Next.js App Router | `77-nextjs.mdc` |
| Result type | neverthrow (or fixed-variance Result) | `73-result-rop.mdc` |
| Contracts | zod | `74-contracts-zod.mdc` |
| Architecture | hexagonal layers | `72-hexagonal-boundaries.mdc` |

These are not re-litigated. Implementation Plans assume them.

